model_metadata.model_description: A two-layer semi-local GRACE model, pre-fitted on the OMat24 and fine-tuned on sAlex+MPTraj datasets, with fixed 6 Å cutoff.
PET-MAD v1.0 model trained on the MAD dataset, which contains 95,595 structures, including 3D and 2D inorganic crystals, surfaces, molecular crystals, nanoclusters, and molecules.
